Original authors and contributors
----------------------------------

The transaction balancing algorithm was designed and implemented
primarily by:

  Jonathan Knowles          — balance algorithm, surplus distribution,
                              size estimation, coin selection integration
  Matthias Benkort (KtorZ)  — transaction balancing design
  Pawel Jakubas             — transaction balancing

With contributions from:

  Heinrich Apfelmus         — transaction balancing
  Johannes Lund (Anviking)  — early transaction construction
  Yura (Unisay)             — transaction balancing

